ffee22ba","tid":935714,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次19係認真直擊水都唔抽&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c001438992408087425831ad0b2c71a86e14d3","tid":935714,"uid":185045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"完全0負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b760737f3df88ef049aaa62e2c165310f3fe8176","tid":935714,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181210&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59012869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181210%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59012869&d=qXvIiLPhcgzIZTgxll1D%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f85ab533\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181210%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59012869&h=167ba44c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181210&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59012869</a><br />\n華為副董事長孟晚舟被加拿大有關當局拘捕後，事件終於有新進展，《華爾街日報》引述消息人士透露，華為近年通知多家機構，並未有透過其總部於香港的企業Skycom Tech於伊朗做生意，有關資訊誤導了多間金融機構，包括滙控及渣打。<br />\n報道引述加拿大法院文件指，除滙控及渣打之外，尚有三家全球性銀行被華為員工或代表誤導，當中一份文件顯示，滙控其中一名代表與孟晚舟於2013年一次會面，孟晚舟帶同一名英文翻譯出席有關會面，並帶上一份以中文寫的Powerpoint進行發言，滙控董事其後收到相關文件的英文翻譯，指孟晚舟華為符合國際制裁的措施，並已出售早前持有SKycom的股份，而公司與其關係是「一般商務合作」。<br />\n加拿大檢控官指，孟晚舟與華為代表意圖誤導銀行，令有關公司可將金錢從受制裁國家透過國際金融體系中移走。華為發言人未有評論有關消息。<br />\n根據Dealogic資料顯示，滙控及渣打是華為最大兩家融資行，過去10年於華為融資項目中扮演重要的角色。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">銀莊既古惑野，心撚照啦！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/10/151624_60cf13272bf91bbaceb1e3a776a029d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F10%2F151624_60cf13272bf91bbaceb1e3a776a029d5.png&h=974cc920&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/10/151950_5ebae96801b44278342e77dc30bd5ee7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F10%2F151950_5ebae96801b44278342e77dc30bd5ee7.png&h=c17871d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a023618a72a9ea0e53d74a47bc9e28fb836d05d","tid":935714,"uid":125470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"94b194ec863d384afd38eef4b9095b34e6fa8eb5","tid":935714,"uid":35776,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"quote":{"pid":"b27ebba5a2ed88a2b303f182f6bb817a3cf72835","tid":935714,"uid":166032,"like":54,"dislike":6,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"19好少咁義正嚴詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"100%冇講其他野冇抽水記憶中冇幾多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"19: 今次4條A 你開出黎見我"},{"pid":"c28f50cb8fe0328bae3dd124ca0039ad6d5e6af3","tid":935714,"uid":7790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:42:55.000Z","msg":"幾時去日本要簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85f4a234f2aea511eaafa56430c26641070f3d1","tid":935714,"uid":51814,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"林奠: 現時政府正全力處理北角車禍，對中央政府有信心可解決華為事件"},{"pid":"a97fe34c783e0cf28cc000070e731178f2794219","tid":935714,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi